summary: A means to store and transfer items through areas of skyrim
descriptionHtml:
[list][*]This mod was made for me by a friend it was designed based on specifications I had given him.
[/*]
[*] 
[/*]
[*]Dark Citzen a.k.a. Duck built this mod and I Crystal Leilani Gonzalez have beta tested this mod. 
[/*]
[*]
[/*]
[*]Once you have purchased breezehome and the cooking pot you make your meals, you will find on the table in front of it an amulet that when worn will give you the option to choose one of the chests, the homes in skyrim you can buy.
[/*]
[*]
[/*]
[*]Once you have chosen which chest you want the contents to be moved to your second option is to then choose from any one of the other chests to have the contents moved. 
[/*]
[*]
[/*]
[*]If you have any questions or find anything wrong with this mod let me know, I'd be happy to help. http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/6220032/?rim/users/6220032/?
[/*]
[/list]
